## android/local.properties.example
## Copy this file to android/local.properties and fill in your values.
## NEVER commit android/local.properties — it contains machine-specific paths and secrets.

## ── Required: Android SDK path ─────────────────────────────────────────────
## Windows default:
sdk.dir=C\:/Users/<YOUR_USERNAME>/AppData/Local/Android/Sdk
## macOS default:
# sdk.dir=/Users/<YOUR_USERNAME>/Library/Android/sdk
## Linux default:
# sdk.dir=/home/<YOUR_USERNAME>/Android/Sdk

## ── Optional: Google Maps Android API key ───────────────────────────────────
## Only needed for Android native map rendering.
## Get your key from: https://console.cloud.google.com/
## Enable: Maps SDK for Android
## Restrict to: Android apps + your package name (com.peedom.mobile)
# ANDROID_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=AIza...
